languages.text: "Чем так воня... пахнет из вашей кельи? Вы там фенрисийский мьод варите? Я слышала о нем, вот бы хоть каплю попробовать!"
"What is that stink— er, rich aroma coming from your cell? Are you brewing Fenrisian mjod in there? I've heard of the stuff — I wouldn't say no to a taste!"

languages.text: “是什么东西这么臭——呃，散发着如此浓郁的芬芳？从你的房间里传出来的吗？你该不会是在里面酿芬里斯蜜酒吧？我听说过那玩意，我很愿意尝尝！”
languages.original_text: "What is that stink— er, rich aroma coming from your cell? Are you brewing Fenrisian mjod in there? I've heard of the stuff — I wouldn't say no to a taste!"

traits.locale_text: “是什么东西这么臭——呃，散发着如此浓郁的芬芳？从你的房间里传出来的吗？你该不会是在里面酿芬里斯蜜酒吧？我听说过那玩意，我很愿意尝尝！”

languages.text: « C'est quoi, cette puan— je veux dire, cette puissante odeur vient de votre cellule, non ? Vous seriez pas en train de brasser votre propre mjod fenrissien, par hasard ? J'en ai entendu parler... et je serais pas contre un petit verre, histoire de goûter ! »
languages.original_text: "What is that stink— er, rich aroma coming from your cell? Are you brewing Fenrisian mjod in there? I've heard of the stuff — I wouldn't say no to a taste!"

languages.text: "Was ist das für ein Gestank ... ähm, Duft, der da aus Eurer Zelle kommt? Braut Ihr da drin etwa fenrisischen Mjod? Davon habe ich schon gehört ... ich hätte nichts gegen eine kleine Kostprobe!"

languages.text: 「何なの、この悪臭…ええと、あなたの部屋から漂ってくる豊な芳香は？フェンリス・ミョードでも作っているの？聞いたことがあるわ。味見なら断らないわよ！」
languages.original_text: "What is that stink— er, rich aroma coming from your cell? Are you brewing Fenrisian mjod in there? I've heard of the stuff — I wouldn't say no to a taste!"

traits.locale_text: 「何なの、この悪臭…ええと、あなたの部屋から漂ってくる豊な芳香は？フェンリス・ミードでも作っているの？聞いたことがあるわ。味見なら断らないわよ！」

languages.text: «¿Qué es esa pes... ese aroma? ¿Viene de tu celda? ¿Estás elaborando mjod fenrisiano? He oído hablar de él... ¡y me gustaría probarlo!».
languages.original_text: "What is that stink— er, rich aroma coming from your cell? Are you brewing Fenrisian mjod in there? I've heard of the stuff — I wouldn't say no to a taste!"

languages.text: "Ne kokusu bu? Bu güzel koku senin hücrenden mi geliyor? İçeride Fenris mjodu mu mayalıyorsun? Adını duymuştum, bir denemeye hayır demem!"
